These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pomegranate
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, bluemaster, aristoff
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
3. the montecristo-smoker is the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
5. the bluemaster-smoker is the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | pomegranate | cauliflower | pineapple |
| Cigar    | bluemaster    | aristoff | montecristo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking
3 different pets are kept: mouse, dog, guinea-pig
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the owner of the dog is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | drawing | filmmaking | board-games |
| Pet   | guinea-pig    | dog     | mouse        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, photography, sudoku
3 different games are played: poker, whist, chess
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing poker##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | photography | baking |
| Game   | whist | poker     | chess  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, quad-bike, tram
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse
1. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Transport   | tram | quad-bike  | snowmobile  |
| Sport         | biathlon  | cricket | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, chaman, oliveros
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, dutch
1. the oliveros-smoker is between the bongani-smoker and the canadian##2
2. the chaman-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the dutch is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Cigar         | bongani   | oliveros | chaman    |
| Nationality   | colombian | dutch     | canadian |

