.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, thriller, crime
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | crime | fantasy   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

