.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, sunflower, poppy
3 different pets are kept: dog, goat, turtle
1. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is between the owner of the turtle and the person who growspoppy##2
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
4. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Flower   | poppy | daisy | sunflower |
| Pet           | goat         | dog         | turtle |

