.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, january, february
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Birthday   | february   | january  | may  |
| Sport         | tennis | lacrosse | climbing |

