2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Sport   | badminton  | weightlifting     | snowboarding |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | jazz    |

