.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, action, western
1. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
2. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | soy-milk |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | western          | epic |

