.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, mystery, epic
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the person watching epic movies is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Movie-Genre     | mystery  | epic   | sports |
| Sport   | lacrosse | handball | golf       |

 